# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:15
translate spanish adrian2b_fe1843ee:

    # "After work, I check the address that Adrian had sent me and put it into the GPS."
    "Después del trabajo, compruebo la dirección que me envió Adrian y la introduzco en el GPS."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:16
translate spanish adrian2b_220b39e6:

    # "It doesn't take long to get to her house. She actually lives really close to my home."
    "No tardo mucho en llegar a su casa. De hecho, vive muy cerca de la mía."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:20
translate spanish adrian2b_614acdee:

    # "I park on the street, then walk up to the front door and knock. A woman answers almost immediately."
    "Aparco en la calle, luego camino hasta la puerta principal y llamo. Una mujer responde casi de inmediato."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:21
translate spanish adrian2b_3dafc9b9:

    # "Woman" "Hello? Can I help you?"
    "Woman" "¿Hola? ¿Puedo ayudarte?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:22
translate spanish adrian2b_966e8fef:

    # pc "I'm looking for Adrian. Does she live here?"
    pc "Busco a Adrian. ¿Vive aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:23
translate spanish adrian2b_b542dd0a:

    # "Woman" "Yes she does."
    "Woman" "Sí, vive aquí."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:24
translate spanish adrian2b_acfd1a5a:

    # pc "She invited me over to play some video games."
    pc "Me ha invitado a venir a jugar a los videojuegos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:25
translate spanish adrian2b_172cc6dd:

    # "Woman" "Oh she did? She didn't tell me that anybody was coming."
    "Woman" "¿Ah, sí? No me había dicho que viniera nadie."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:26
translate spanish adrian2b_2fdb51d6:

    # "Woman" "You just stay there and I'll go get her."
    "Woman" "Quédate ahí y voy a buscarla."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:27
translate spanish adrian2b_cddf2662:

    # "Then, I hear footsteps coming down the stairs and Adrian calls out."
    "Entonces, oigo pasos bajando las escaleras y Adrian grita:"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:28
translate spanish adrian2b_9899eaa9:

    # gg "He's my friend, Mom, let him in."
    gg "Es mi amigo, mamá, déjalo pasar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:33
translate spanish adrian2b_c583a608:

    # "Woman" "You're supposed to tell me if somebody is coming over, Adrian."
    "Woman" "Se supone que tienes que decirme si viene alguien, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:34
translate spanish adrian2b_6c01d4fd:

    # gg "I know, Mom. I meant to, but I was just busy... with schoolwork. I forgot."
    gg "Lo sé, mamá. Tenía intención de hacerlo, pero estaba ocupado... con los deberes. Se me olvidó."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:35
translate spanish adrian2b_e878210c:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "Okay, well he can stay until 10."
    "Adrian's Mom" "Vale, pues puede quedarse hasta las 10."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:36
translate spanish adrian2b_326f12bf:

    # gg "Okay, Mom. Thank you."
    gg "Vale, mamá. Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:39
translate spanish adrian2b_8f7ebec7:

    # "I follow her inside the house and we walk up the stairs."
    "La sigo dentro de la casa y subimos las escaleras."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:44
translate spanish adrian2b_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/adrian_sorry.mp3'
    voice 'voices/adrian_sorry.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:45
translate spanish adrian2b_c03425eb:

    # gg "I'm sorry about that. She can be a bit overbearing sometimes."
    gg "Lo siento por eso. A veces puede ser un poco autoritaria."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:46
translate spanish adrian2b_3ed1d973:

    # gg "She's just very protective of me. Only child and all."
    gg "Es que es muy protectora conmigo. Soy hija única y todo eso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:49
translate spanish adrian2b_04c7f126:

    # pc "My dad could be the same way sometimes when I was growing up. I'm an only child too."
    pc "Mi padre a veces era igual cuando era pequeña. Yo también soy hija única."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:50
translate spanish adrian2b_f7e6c62b:

    # gg "Then you understand."
    gg "Entonces lo entiendes."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:52
translate spanish adrian2b_636661b2:

    # gg "It does sometimes."
    gg "A veces pasa."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:53
translate spanish adrian2b_2900eca8:

    # gg "But I love her and she's been really good to me through a lot of hard times."
    gg "Pero la quiero y ha sido muy buena conmigo en muchos momentos difíciles."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:54
translate spanish adrian2b_c07d0332:

    # pc "That's good. Always good to have people there for you."
    pc "Eso está bien. Siempre es bueno tener gente que te apoye."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:55
translate spanish adrian2b_a560b57e:

    # gg "Want to check out the game?"
    gg "¿Quieres echarle un vistazo al juego?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:56
translate spanish adrian2b_39757b54:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do it."
    pc "Sí, vamos a ello."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:59
translate spanish adrian2b_5c242d3c:

    # gg "Okay, so this is my character. Her name is Trenoxa and she's a mage."
    gg "Vale, este es mi personaje. Se llama Trenoxa y es una maga."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:60
translate spanish adrian2b_290fa501:

    # pc "She looks badass."
    pc "Tiene pinta de dura."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:61
translate spanish adrian2b_eecdf621:

    # gg "Oh she definitely is. Watch me kill all these kobolds."
    gg "Oh, sin duda lo es. Mira cómo mato a todos estos kobolds."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:66
translate spanish adrian2b_8a0ec2b0:

    # "Using the keyboard and mouse, she guides her character into the middle of a group of small monsters and proceeds to blow them all up."
    "Con el teclado y el ratón, guía a su personaje hasta el centro de un grupo de pequeños monstruos y procede a hacerlos volar por los aires."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:68
translate spanish adrian2b_c9d9899a:

    # "I barely look at the screen, unable to take my eyes off of her."
    "Apenas miro la pantalla, incapaz de apartar la vista de ella."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:69
translate spanish adrian2b_c68ec5f4:

    # "She really gets into this stuff, and it's cute to see her so excited about it."
    "Se mete de lleno en esto, y es bonito verla tan emocionada."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:72
translate spanish adrian2b_f57aeacc:

    # gg "Do you want to give it a try?"
    gg "¿Quieres probarlo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:73
translate spanish adrian2b_e3e97310:

    # pc "What if I get your character killed?"
    pc "¿Y si mato a tu personaje?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:74
translate spanish adrian2b_03db2857:

    # gg "It's no big deal. You just revive at the nearest respawn point and are weakened for a few minutes."
    gg "No pasa nada. Simplemente revives en el punto de reaparición más cercano y estás debilitado durante unos minutos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:75
translate spanish adrian2b_9a5eb084:

    # gg "Come on, give it a try, see if you like it."
    gg "Venga, pruébalo, a ver si te gusta."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:76
translate spanish adrian2b_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:79
translate spanish adrian2b_2d53ff69:

    # "We switch seats and I play for a bit, trying to learn all the buttons."
    "Cambiamos de sitio y juego un rato, intentando aprenderme todos los botones."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:80
translate spanish adrian2b_b0a6ba6f:

    # gg "Okay, all of your powers are the number keys up top. You move with WASD and look around with the mouse."
    gg "Vale, todos tus poderes están en las teclas numéricas de arriba. Te mueves con WASD y miras a tu alrededor con el ratón."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:81
translate spanish adrian2b_3b25da4f:

    # gg "Just click on what you want to kill and then use one of your powers to kill it."
    gg "Solo tienes que hacer clic en lo que quieras matar y luego usar uno de tus poderes para acabar con ello."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:82
translate spanish adrian2b_b4a8a49d:

    # gg "Super easy. Barely an inconvenience."
    gg "Súper fácil. Apenas supone un inconveniente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:83
translate spanish adrian2b_babb66b4:

    # pc "You say that, but I'm still wondering what a WASD is."
    pc "Tú dices eso, pero yo sigo preguntándome qué es eso de WASD."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:86
translate spanish adrian2b_055f2992:

    # "A little bit later, I have pretty much figured out the controls and am demolishing enemies."
    "Un rato después, ya me he hecho bastante a la idea de los controles y estoy arrasando con los enemigos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:87
translate spanish adrian2b_4915d075:

    # gg "You like it?"
    gg "¿Te gusta?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:88
translate spanish adrian2b_3b7f3448:

    # pc "I have to admit, it's pretty fun."
    pc "Tengo que admitir que es bastante divertido."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:89
translate spanish adrian2b_a82592f5:

    # gg "I'm glad. If you bought a copy sometime, we could even play together."
    gg "Me alegro. Si alguna vez te compras una copia, podríamos incluso jugar juntos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:90
translate spanish adrian2b_c0437e5d:

    # pc "That would be fun."
    pc "Eso sería divertido."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:93
translate spanish adrian2b_ee920117:

    # gg "I think so too. I'd love to explore and kill goblins with you."
    gg "Yo también lo creo. Me encantaría explorar y matar goblins contigo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:94
translate spanish adrian2b_efa756f8:

    # pc "Maybe I'll get it sometime then."
    pc "Quizá me lo compre algún día, entonces."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:95
translate spanish adrian2b_ce14f6da:

    # gg "Good."
    gg "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:96
translate spanish adrian2b_6a346fe1:

    # gg "It's about time for you to go. I wouldn't mind hanging out longer, but it's nearly 10 and my mom will be mad."
    gg "Ya es hora de que te vayas. No me importaría quedarme más rato, pero son casi las 10 y mi madre se enfadará."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:97
translate spanish adrian2b_8f70c6ec:

    # pc "Okay, I'll go then. Don't want to get you in trouble."
    pc "Vale, me voy entonces. No quiero meterte en problemas."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:98
translate spanish adrian2b_45175d50:

    # gg "I had a good time though. Thank you for coming over."
    gg "Pero lo he pasado muy bien. Gracias por venir."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:99
translate spanish adrian2b_1b5489ad:

    # pc "Thanks for inviting me, I had fun too."
    pc "Gracias por invitarme, yo también me lo he pasado bien."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:103
translate spanish adrian2b_6a658ffa:

    # "She walks me down to the front door."
    "Me acompaña hasta la puerta principal."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:104
translate spanish adrian2b_2c7e0e7e:

    # gg "I could probably get you a copy of the game. If I did, would you play with me?"
    gg "Probablemente podría conseguirte una copia del juego. Si lo hiciera, ¿jugarías conmigo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:105
translate spanish adrian2b_7f0c6c37:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I could do that."
    pc "Sí, creo que podría hacerlo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:107
translate spanish adrian2b_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/adrian_seeyou.mp3'
    voice 'voices/adrian_seeyou.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:108
translate spanish adrian2b_c8b2cdfc:

    # gg "Okay cool. I'll see you in class, [pcname]."
    gg "Vale, genial. Nos vemos en clase, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:109
translate spanish adrian2b_9bfc226b:

    # pc "Alright. Bye, Adrian."
    pc "De acuerdo. Adiós, Adrian."

